  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d4e9470&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePw3ZeGRruzib6uAZIwnice3OuOOI6Kb8X6dFlWpZWiaKic2p2Jk4d5GicMaRbaAqvDEpOIH818qqAYKicNEo5voykBg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"逛逛GitHub\" data-alias=\"ggGithub\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ePw3ZeGRruyXo8VzACicO8MVibibicuJUQ8Vzghx6WF8F51breYjBIuYd4cj6wp26BYrg850bNuA20rdic9UyKIUhpg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"热门「开源项目」推送到你眼前，每日为你节省 1 小时。 给我发消息可咨询各种开源项目，专注 AI、硬科技开源领域。\" data-id=\"MzUxNjg4NDEzNA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjejcnc65ga\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjejftlltom\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjek1tg521n8\">Vibe Coding 说白了就是开发个应用不再像程序员一样，苦哈哈地写每一行代码，而是化身为导演。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span mpa-font-style=\"mjek1tg5qvg\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">只需要<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">保持一种感觉</span>，这种感觉可能是对产品逻辑、用户流程、审美和交互的把握，剩下的体力活全交给 Cursor、Windsurf、Trae 等 AI 编程工具。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span mpa-font-style=\"mjek1tg5yrj\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">用 Karpathy 的话说：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">我几乎不写代码了，我只负责调整氛围（Vibe），代码会自动长出来。</span></span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span mpa-font-style=\"mjejftllse0\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/ePw3ZeGRruzib6uAZIwnice3OuOOI6Kb8XCrJRdHhGufHA3E01VKk92Hm8ibicAJQ1JczFPFDBtXlmrq3RMAmdaoXA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1024\" data-cropy1=\"157.67474048442907\" data-cropy2=\"891.1280276816609\" data-imgfileid=\"100046170\" data-ratio=\"0.716796875\" style=\"width: 578px;height: 414px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7bbbb5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FePw3ZeGRruzib6uAZIwnice3OuOOI6Kb8X7crQiaY9oD4ASLkbm2vTBDZMFKEM4g1PCaRrlBhLKcbPElVmqOt7kyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></s